{"tid":446154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳現共享貓咪 網民鬧爆：為賺錢瘋了","createTime":"2017-10-24T05:06:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T08:29:23.000Z","uid":88681,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4cefeb8de02eefff36e55238f9d9d7512850660b","tid":446154,"uid":88681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T05:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171023/large/1508748424_5a56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171023%2Flarge%2F1508748424_5a56.jpg&h=e304f05a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要加上「共享」，就可以為一切商業行為再包裝？深圳一間貓店近日推出「共享貓咪」服務，只要付出2,500元（人民幣．下同）按金，便可以用39.9元（約47港元）租金，租用貓咪一日，以「滿足部分貓友的需求」。可是，這服務卻被網民鬧爆，稱貓咪不斷轉換環境，對他們實在有害，同時大批網民舉報這貓店，其微博已找不到租貓的內容。<br />\n<br />\n這間貓店名為「深圳吉祥貓舍」，位於龍崗區，早前該店在網上推出租貓服務，聲稱這服務是為「滿足部分貓友的需求」，同時稱解決「孩子是不是一時興起想養純種貓而苦惱」、「日後可能出差無法照顧好貓咪而裹足不前」、「是否真的適合養貓而發愁」等問題。貓店稱，除了要付按金，還要簽訂「出租協議」，聲稱貓店在開始及結束租用期時都會做貓瘟測試，確保貓咪健康，同時若發現客人虐貓，就不會退還款項。租客要付按金，租金會在按金中扣除，交還時退回餘額，如果租用期太長，租金超越按金時，貓咪便直接歸客人所有。<br />\n「貓咪是一個活物啊，不像單車啥的是個物體！」不少人都批評活生生的生物，不可能隨便當成商品租用，有網民更稱「現在的人想賺錢想瘋了！」「貓的領地意識非常強，對於頻繁更換的陌生環境會很敏感，甚至會產生應激反應，長期嚴重的應激反應會直接導致貓的死亡！」於是有網民向各個社交媒體、網上商業平台和當地的工商局舉報。<br />\n貓店相關的內容已經被刪除，但也有網民質疑整個事件都只是一場炒作。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171023/57367198\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171023%2F57367198&d=%2BhKbYXjbfNW7K7L3fU1Sdv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=78058e66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171023%2F57367198&h=b5f99df5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171023/57367198</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 衰過貓cafe"},{"pid":"e0a5d1a98be8a49ffe36236238e2f909f69e619c","tid":446154,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T05:08:02.000Z","msg":"pt家貓"},{"pid":"0d4f22b82823ec7203c3bafeb7652cd7dd9e226e","tid":446154,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T05:12:40.000Z","msg":"共享女友=叫雞"},{"pid":"08865b690e78c955e29817b65ec07659fb4a98b8","tid":446154,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T05:13:22.000Z","msg":"如果租用期太長，租金超越按金時，貓咪便直接歸客人所有。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81eeec8523c80640d61a8161b5ddb8a5f9e2e23","tid":446154,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T05:15:20.000Z","msg":"ptcf<br />\n<br />\npart time cat friend"},{"pid":"42a7fbc6e70eafec6a891ba74d521a29b74a4e8e","tid":446154,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T05:38:47.000Z","msg":"Part time pet cat"},{"pid":"a047c2994ec2a409eb3ed1ae66e344510563a3b3","tid":446154,"uid":1767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T05:43:11.000Z","msg":"又黎按金 成$2500 一走佬就發過豬頭丙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb10b4fffdf4727eab157a2a930b69a6568fe1b","tid":446154,"uid":148531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T06:25:56.000Z","msg":"有無得共享chocolat vanilla<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b637eff26e7128027ff86687d70f15c0601c93b9","tid":446154,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T06:39:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又黎按金 成$2500 一走佬就發過豬頭丙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁先識玩"},{"pid":"324b11240b0d342610e06687583d827bda56c169","tid":446154,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>共享女友=叫雞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫雞嗰啲好似叫共享肉便器<br />\n<br />\n共享女友應該係ptgf"},{"pid":"3f48e5975f50e730e4e428